project_descr: Support to the Ethiopian  Mine Action Programme in Afar, Tigray and Somali Regions to free Mine infected land, provide Mine Risk Education and comply to the Mine Ban Treaty

outputs.output_descr: The purpose of this project is to demine and ensure the continuation of demining activities in the most affected communities of Tigray, Afar and Somali regions for improved safety and food security of the community, while improving and accelerating the demining capacity of Ethiopian Mine Action Office.

project_title: mine action in tigray and afar regions of ethiopia
